        <p>Click the down arrow to open a small window. In this window, you can enter the size of the font in the lower-left field (either type a number or use the up and down arrows). You can select the unit of measurement (e.g., pixels, points, centimeters) using the lower-right drop-down arrow. <MadCap:conditionalText MadCap:conditions="General.OnlineLive">See <MadCap:xref href="../../../Styles/More_About_Styles_and_Style_Sheets/About_Units_of_Measurement.htm">About Units of Measurement</MadCap:xref>. </MadCap:conditionalText>You can return to the default setting by using the upper-right drop-down arrow.</p>
